                        <h1> Specialty Leasing</h1>

<h3>Eglinton Square Shopping Centre Specialty Leasing</h3>

<p>Our cart/kiosk/in-line program is for seasonal, established and/or new retailers alike! The program is flexible and affordable enough for even first-time retailers to test the market for their new or one-of-a-kind product(s).</p>

<p>***All Eglinton Square Retailers must have a business license and provide insurance.***</p>

<p>The specialty leasing program at&nbsp;Eglinton Square is run by&nbsp;Cart Wheels International Inc.</p>

<p>For more information regarding the Specialty Leasing program,&nbsp;contact:</p>

<p>Susan Dennis&nbsp;of Cart Wheels International Inc.&nbsp;by telephone at 905-855-1616 or 1-800-236-1591, by fax at 905-855-1613,&nbsp;or by email at <a href="mailto:cartwheels@on.aibn.com">cartwheels@on.aibn.com</a>.</p>

<p>For more information regarding Cart Wheels International Inc., visit their website at <a href="http://www.cartwheelsinternational.com">www.cartwheelsinternational.com</a>.</p>

<h3>RMUs (CARTS)</h3>

<p>The cart program offers you minimum overhead in a highly visible location and offers your product exposure at very affordable rates. All carts are subject to availability.</p>

<h3>COMMON AREA</h3>

<p>Do you have a unique display you’d like to show off? Bring your specialized display to&nbsp;Eglinton Square Shopping Centre. Typical kiosk set-up at Eglinton Square is 10 X 12.&nbsp; The common area program offers your product exposure at very affordable rates. All&nbsp;common area set-up must first be approved by Cart Wheels and is&nbsp;&nbsp;subject availability of space.</p>

<h3>IN-LINE</h3>

<p>Looking to give a store front location a try? Big or small, Eglinton Square could be the new location of that next big thing, YOU! Sizes and availability vary. You will be responsible for paying for utilities.</p>

<h2>OUTSIDE ADVERTISING:</h2>

<h3>LARGE FORMAT ADVERTISING/NEO-TRAFFIC</h3>

<p>An industry leader in large format advertising, Neo Traffic is an excellent company to run a large format campaign through. Contact them at 1-877-326-4456&nbsp;and mention you’d like to run a&nbsp;large format campaign at Eglinton Square for interior/exterior&nbsp;–&nbsp;banners, walls or static displays. Visit them on line to see more of their exciting advertising options.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.neo-traffic.com">www.neo-traffic.com</a></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1> Permanent Leasing </h1>

    <h3>Eglinton Square Shopping Centre</h3>

<p>Eglinton Square Shopping Centre is an enclosed shopping centre, located at the corner of Victoria Park and Eglinton Avenue,&nbsp;in Toronto, Ontario, Canada. It was one of the first malls in Toronto, opening in 1954. It is owned by Kingsett Capital and managed by Bentall Kennedy (Canada) LP. It has approximately 279,000 sq ft (25,900 m2) of retail space with over 80 retail outlets including two anchor tenants in Metro and The Bay, a food court, bank, and a branch of the Toronto Public Library</p>

<h3><strong>Major Tenants:</strong></h3>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;">The Bay</p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Metro</p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Shoppers Drug Mart</p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Dollarama</p>

